data.name: label7.ToolTip
data.value:
This randomizes the special(blue) boxes on each track.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Can be placed higher, changed to a Weapon(red) Shop box, or both.
SPORADIC - Good luck finding these. Completely random.

data.name: label3.ToolTip
data.value:
This randomizes the weapon(red) boxes on each track.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Can be placed higher, changed to a Special(blue) Shop box, or both.
SPORADIC - Good luck finding these. Completely random.

data.name: label1.ToolTip
data.value:
This randomizes the coins on each track.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Randomly sets coins higher than their initial position if on the ground, or lower in the air if in the air.
SPORADIC - Good luck finding coins. Completely randomized.

data.name: comboBox1.ToolTip
data.value:
This randomizes the track coin locations on each track.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Throws coins high enough only to jump and grab them, or hides them from being collected.
SPORADIC - Anything goes.

data.name: label5.ToolTip
data.value:
Randomizes the Snowmen for Shot Game.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Turns snowmen, facing random directions. Places them higher, requiring jumps to shoot them.
PICK-UPS - Randomizes the snowmen to be placed where coins, weapon shops, special shops and speed game fans would be located on the track.

data.name: label6.ToolTip
data.value:
Randomizes the Fans for Speed Game.
VANILLA - Original Game Settings.
BASIC - Randomly places them higher, requiring jumps to shoot them.
PICK-UPS - Randomizes the fans to be placed where coins, weapon shops, special shops and shot game snowmen would be located on the track.

data.name: label9.ToolTip
data.value:
Randomizes the score to beat in order to get the Feather Board to show up in the store for purchase.
VANILLA - Unchanged requirement.
SAFE - Randomizes between 0-1700
IDIOTIC - Completely random value, up to 65,535. Will also adjust the time required accordingly.
